definition: orchid (蘭花|兰花 Cymbidium goeringii)/fragrant thoroughwort (蘭草|兰草 Eupatorium fortunei)/lily magnolia (木蘭|木兰)
surname Lan/abbr. for Lanzhou 蘭州|兰州[Lan2 zhou1], Gansu

sentences.english: Project only for those, who have Suomi as mother language.
sentences.chinese: 只對那些項目，誰作爲母語芬蘭語。

sentences.english: Yes, I speak only a little bit of Finnish.
sentences.chinese: 是的，我只能說一點點芬蘭語。

sentences.english: However, the Finnish language bears some similarities to the Sami language.
sentences.chinese: 然而芬蘭語和薩米語有一些相似處。

sentences.english: For example, I actually learned Finnish.
sentences.chinese: 比方，我真的學會了芬蘭語。
